        {
            "title": "五角大樓據悉算出伊朗戰爭賬 估算首周耗資逾113億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"五角大樓據悉算出伊朗戰爭賬 估算首周耗資逾113億美元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BeJncwuSq8pYO5uLFTda5A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-08/7afbe4b0-511b-11ef-9cf3-617f0878b04a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">五角大樓據悉算出伊朗戰爭賬 估算首周耗資逾113億美元</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
