            "title": "摩根大通因競爭及投資壓力下調MercadoLibre評級",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"摩根大通\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:摩根大通;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根大通\">摩根大通</a>將MercadoLibre評級從增持下調至中性,並將目標價從2,650美元下調至2,100美元,理由是巴西市場競爭持續激烈,且預期該公司在繼續投資增長的同時,利潤率將持續承壓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巴西的競爭局勢並未緩和,而MercadoLibre已表明願意在短期內接受較低的利潤率,以優先進行投資。<br/><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Sea Limited旗下電商部門Shopee繼續在巴西追求增長,即使這需要犧牲利潤率。<br/><br/>Shopee最近的言論顯示,該公司計劃將調整費率結構所節省的資金,再投資於與巴西即時支付系統Pix相關的折讓。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-326e8fbb-cd61-3331-8843-4170c4739f3f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通在MercadoLibre首席財務官表示該公司在短期內對約9%的利潤率感到滿意後,下調了其盈利能力展望。摩根大通分析師將2026年利潤率預估下調至8.8%,目前預期息稅前盈利將較2026年市場共識預測低約15%,較2026年第一季預期低約24%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通還將長期利潤率假設從17%下調至14%,理由是在戰略投資持續進行的情況下,盈利能力何時恢復的能見度有限。該公司表示,預計2026年利潤率將下降約1.8個百分點,因該公司專注於擴展其平台。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此,該分析師表示MercadoLibre在拉丁美洲電商和金融科技市場的長期定位仍然良好。<br/><br/>該券商預期2026年至2029年間盈利將以約32%的複合年增長率增長,但表示鑑於利潤率面臨的短期壓力,投資者在2026年不太可能將該長期展望納入定價考量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E5%9B%A0%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFmercadolibre%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-152024564.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 00:07:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "債券交易員不再押注聯儲會2026年降息一次的概率為100%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 債券交易員已不再押注聯儲會在2026年降息的概率為100%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與聯儲會政策會議日期掛鉤的利率互換合約顯示，交易員周四押注的今年降息幅度僅為24個基點，這相當於進行一次幅度為25個基點降息的可能性不到100%。周三晚些時候，交易員押注的降息幅度約為30個基點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一轉變正值美國國債延續近期跌勢，其中對聯儲會政策變化最為敏感的兩年期國債殖利率上漲4個基點，接近3.70%。本周，由於投資者擔心中東衝突將持續推高能源價格，導致通膨再度抬頭，美國國債承壓。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0f8661d8-98d2-3fb6-b5ca-975ccea3a810-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，本周各公司大量發行新債，同時美國財政部將於紐約時間下午1點發行220億美元的30年期國債。本周早些時候的3年期和10年期國債標售遇疲軟需求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Traders Are No Longer Fully Pricing In a Fed Rate Cut This Year</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%832026%E5%B9%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-%E6%AC%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E7%82%BA100-151833300.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 00:07:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
